              <text><citation jurisdiction="nz">Section 9(6)</citation> is amended by omitting <amend.in>in <citation jurisdiction="nz">subsection (5)</citation></amend.in> and substituting <amend.in>in the definition of <emphasis style="bold">deal with</emphasis> in <citation jurisdiction="nz">section 4</citation></amend.in>.</text>
            </para>
